creator: Christian Crusaders
descriptionHtml:
Home of Christian Crusaders, which has been producing Bible-based worship services and Christian content since 1936.

Our CC Broadcasts have our weekly services: half-hour broadcasts over the radio and internet featuring sermons by Revs. Steve Kramer and Lee Laaveg.

Our CC Podcasts section features two separate streams. Conversations are in-depth interviews that will inspire you and urge a deeper dive in your faith. The Daily Dose Devotions are 6 minute messages from our staff or our partner ministries' staff which are uploaded daily and which examine a different topic each season. Season 1 were inspirational messages to help us get through the early days of the changing public health situation in 2020. Season 2 is an overview of the Bible, focusing on an application to our daily lives today.

Our app also features resources that help you get connected or get assistance in your faith journey.
descriptionShort: Bible-based worship services and podcasts produced daily
